applicationProfileDefinition.en: Self-contained Expression that uniquely and fully expresses Individual Work.
The Independent Expression that expresses the Work.

applicationProfileUsageNote.en: E.g. the Work is expressed by means of a text, music, etc. If the Work is an Individual Work, then there is one and no more than one Independent Expression that fully expresses the Work. If it is a Complex Work, the Independent Expression expresses a Work that is part of the Complex Work. In the case of a Container Work (e.g. a Publication Work), the Independent Expression expresses this work or another work that is included in it (e.g. a photograph in a book).
